      <h2>About CourseDash</h2>
      <p>
        CourseDash is a lightweight academic dashboard enabling users to manage SAT scores, majors, and notes through dynamic CRUD operations. It integrates real-time data from public APIs, ensures smooth updates with localStorage, and tackles key UI and validation challenges for a seamless user experience.
      </p>

